snippet.title: New WiiU Game Announcement Teaser Trailer | Silver Falls White Inside Its Umbra
snippet.description:
The new entry in the Silver Falls horror series has been officially revealed. White Inside Its Umbra will launch exclusively on Nintendo Wii U. Find out why fans can't get enough of this game series by visiting http://silverfallsgame.com/. Play 2 free entries in the series and read the Heavy Shadow novel for free.

https://www.facebook.com/silverfallsgame/
https://twitter.com/silverfallsgame
